-----------------------------------------------------------------
Solyaris - Visual Movie Browser
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Solyaris is a visual movie browser to find and discover films, 
actors or directors and explore their connections. 

Search the entire Open Movie Database (TMDb) collection for movies 
or people. Expand nodes to gather information about their 
relationships. Learn about the cast and filmography. 

This product uses the TMDb API but is not endorsed or certified by 
TMDb. All information provided by TMDb, IMDb, Rotten Tomatoes, 
YouTube and Wikipedia. Solyaris is not responsible for the content, 
nor the availability or performance of these services.

Made with Cinder.


Project URL:
http://solyaris.cecinestpasparis.net

App Store:
http://itunes.apple.com/app/solyaris-visual-movie-browser/id481963410?mt=8




